{"tid":1865883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥也買不到廁紙","createTime":"2020-02-06T12:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T07:54:35.000Z","uid":297241,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d1494c15f49a374478dc5b64dadeba77e0202b5c","tid":1865883,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"午夜買廁紙 林鄭「敗走」便利店<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】已宣布參選特首的前政務司司長林鄭月娥昨會見傳媒時自爆，近日忙於遷出官邸，本來已經遷入灣仔一個單位，及至<span style=\"color: red;\">午夜發現單位內沒有廁紙，走到附近便利店希望購買一、兩卷廁紙，才發現便利店原來沒有售賣廁紙，</span>最終要乘搭的士返回官邸居住。當問及會否擔心於提名「入閘」後，於屬於「暗票」的投票階段落敗，林鄭間接承認「驚輸」，坦言對此表示擔心，又知悉商界對自己有意見，包括不認識經濟金融、「識使錢唔識賺錢」、搞福利主義等，其後又預告長子或會助選。"},{"pid":"835d433be7d42d7a84c34d21256ed5ed54d81998","tid":1865883,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"我在呢度呼籲巴士、地鐵、航空、入境、同海關工會在2月10日或之前盡快表決通過罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1864623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1864623</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDPGeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDPGeQ.png&h=f227900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家疫情有爆發跡象，十萬火急！藍田女手足全家確診武漢肺炎，請大家幫手簽下面的聯署：<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n另外大家亦可以透過聯署同twitter自行遊說美方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲研發出肺炎解藥的美國藥廠供貨香港救手足救香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=87054c7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n給予港府壓力封閉所有連接中國大陸的口岸<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders